flowchart TD
    In["Telegram message / photo / document"] --> Store["Store MESSAGE immediately"]
    Store --> Ack["Best-effort immediate ack"]
    Ack --> AckFail{"Ack send failed?"}
    AckFail -->|Yes| AckWarn["logger.warning<br/>webhook still returns 200"]
    AckFail -->|No| Accepted["Accepted"]
    AckWarn --> Accepted

    Store --> State["Load CONVERSATION_STATE"]
    State --> Gate{"Deterministic command gate first"}

    Gate -->|Slash command| Slash["Pin intent by command<br/>resolve flexible argument"]
    Gate -->|Natural command request| NLRouter["Natural-language router<br/>map text to internal command"]
    NLRouter --> Slash
    Slash -->|/new| NewNote["Create new NOTE<br/>AI title / summary / tags"]
    Slash -->|/add /fix /delete /dedupe| Approval["Store pending_action<br/>preview + approval required"]
    Slash -->|/list /show over 10| Page["Paginated reply<br/>page_state + /next /prev"]
    Gate -->|Numbered reference| Numbered["Resolve from last_list_results<br/>then last_search_results<br/>set last_selected_note_id"]
    Gate -->|Read original| ReadLast["DB-only lookup<br/>NOTE.body or IMAGE_FILE.ocr_text"]
    Gate -->|Search / Recent / Count| ReadTools["DB-only active NOTE reads<br/>save list/search result state"]
    Gate -->|Correction| Correct["Resolve target<br/>parse replace/delete phrase<br/>update NOTE title/summary/body<br/>and IMAGE_FILE ocr/summary"]
    Gate -->|Delete request| DeleteAsk["Store pending_delete_note_id"]
    Gate -->|Delete confirm| DeleteExec["Idempotent soft delete<br/>deleted_at + deleted_reason"]
    Gate -->|No command| MetaGuard{"Meta-command safety net"}

    MetaGuard -->|Meta command| NoSave["Do not create or append NOTE"]
    MetaGuard -->|Normal content| Prep["Strip explicit save prefixes"]
    Prep --> Context["Load same-chat context<br/>last 30 minutes only"]
    Context --> AIRouter["AI route_text(prepared text)"]

    AIRouter -->|Create| Create["Create NOTE + AI_ANALYSIS<br/>using prepared text"]
    AIRouter -->|Append| Append["Append prepared text<br/>to existing NOTE"]
    AIRouter -->|Ignore| Ignore["Mark processed; no NOTE"]
    AIRouter -->|Tool| Tool["Tags / merge / fallback read tools"]

    In -->|Photo| Photo["Store IMAGE_FILE"]
    Photo --> Vision["OCR + classify"]
    Vision --> ImageUpdate["Update IMAGE_FILE<br/>ocr_text / summary / image_type / confidence"]
    ImageUpdate --> Existing{"Existing NOTE for message/image?"}
    Existing -->|Yes| ExistingRef["Reuse NOTE<br/>set last_image_note_id"]
    Existing -->|No note image| ImageNote["Create NOTE<br/>set last_artifact_note_id + last_image_note_id"]
    Existing -->|Unclear| Review["MESSAGE.status=needs_review"]
    Existing -->|General photo| PhotoOnly["Archive only"]

    In -->|Document / PDF| Document["Store original file<br/>and document metadata"]
    Document --> PageLoop["Process PDF page by page<br/>preserve page numbers"]
    PageLoop --> TextCheck{"Enough embedded text<br/>on this page?"}
    TextCheck -->|Yes| EmbeddedText["Keep parser text"]
    TextCheck -->|No| RenderPage["Render page to image<br/>at OCR resolution"]
    RenderPage --> PageOCR["Vision OCR<br/>using NIM_VISION_MODEL"]
    EmbeddedText --> PageText["Store page text + source type"]
    PageOCR --> PageText
    PageText --> MorePages{"More selected pages?"}
    MorePages -->|Yes| PageLoop
    MorePages -->|No| MergeDoc["Merge in page order<br/>keep page boundaries"]
    MergeDoc --> DocNote["Create NOTE<br/>AI title / summary / tags<br/>preserve file reference"]

    Numbered --> Reply["Best-effort result reply"]
    NewNote --> Reply
    Approval --> Reply
    Page --> Reply
    ReadLast --> Reply
    ReadTools --> Reply
    Correct --> Reply
    DeleteAsk --> Reply
    DeleteExec --> Reply
    NoSave --> Reply
    Create --> Reply
    Append --> Reply
    Ignore --> Reply
    Tool --> Reply
    ExistingRef --> Reply
    ImageNote --> Reply
    Review --> Reply
    PhotoOnly --> Reply
    DocNote --> Reply

    Reply --> ReplyFail{"Result send failed?"}
    ReplyFail -->|Yes| ReplyFailed["MESSAGE.status=reply_failed<br/>logger.warning"]
    ReplyFail -->|No| Done["Keep action status"]
